name: Random Stuff
body:
# What's this?
Sometimes I build random things. Sometimes I want to share them so others can use them if they want. Here you go.

# List of stuff
## [Classroom Scheduler](classroom-scheduler.html)
Coordinating the schedules of students and paras in a single class can be a very time consuming task. This tool tries to help out by showing you the schedule by student and by teacher/para at the same time as you make edits.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
